manifests.contents:
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "ws_client"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "ws_client"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true

[dependencies]
flume = "0.11.0"
futures = "0.3.30"
futures-util = "0.3.30"
serde_json = "1.0.114"
tokio-tungstenite = "0.21.0"
tracing = "0.1.40"

[dependencies.axum]
version = "0.7.4"
features = ["ws"]

[dependencies.clap]
version = "4.5.3"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.197"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.36.0"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3.18"
features = ["env-filter"]

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "ws_client"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []
crate-type = ["rlib"]
